_sText:
This is your standard aim_daegle7k map, but I have made the boxes shift into 12 different possibilities.  4 versions are the same, but the boxes are either switched between CT and T sides or left side and right side have been switched.  The other 8 versions have the boxes re-arranged in different fashions using the original boxes as much as possible.
